	   <tr><td colspan=2>Aloha everyone,<br><br>Just started a new Half Elf Bard in Freeport.  Its such a nice change from my 20 Mage I currently have.  I cant wait to gain mroe songs and learn the Bard tricks.  What I liked about the bard is how the Bard gets almost all skills like dodge, hide, forage, etc.  One skill that role playing wise that would also make sense and be cool to have for bards since they are "Entertainers" is Feign Death.  Feign Death is all about putting on a show to fool your enemy.  It would be great to have so you dont have to have Selo's Accelerando and a drum ready to go all the time.  Mabye give it around 30 ish.  What are your thoughts.<br><br>A fanatically frantic new Bard<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
