	   <tr><td colspan=2>You cannot use instruments until the required lvl.  <br><br>You can ONLY equip instruments if both slots are empty (unless its me), IE.. take out weapon/shield then apply instrument.<br><br>Small (light) brass armor is good, until quest armor.<br><br>I (hear) player made jewelry is the best in the game (proly except for uber drops)<br><br><br>&nbsp;<br>Willowhysp<br>"I will bend like a reed in the wind" (take a guess)</td></tr>
