	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hey peeps! It's you friendly neighborhood lvl 44 Bard here to help with some hot tips and tricks.<br><br>FIRST! Song twisting is easy. Click on a song and count to 5 mississipi. You should see the effect on your chat screen. Then click off and click on the next song. Depending on what songs you are doing it is quite possible to have 5 going at once. Usually 3 is max but some last a bit longer.<br><br>SECOND! Depending on your Stats (CHA, DEX, etc...) would determine what jewlry or OTHER items you should be wearing. At lower lvls it's EASY to get a 'dervish cut throat insignia ring' for DEX boost. There should be no prob getting one of these free.<br><br>THIRD! Bronze is a good armor for the non-twinked bard to start with. Sells for fairly cheap and can even be picked up free if you are in the right zone (Check this website to see where that might be).<br><br>That's all for now. Peace!<br><br>Faredin Songweaver<br>Brell Serilis<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
