	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hello fellow bards and others!<br><br>    Ever wonder what a reall easy way to get your swimming skill up is? Well here it is, Once you get to lvl 18 go learn the song Tawerys Aquatic Lyre, also you will need the lvl 5 song ( i think its lvl 5) Jaxons Jig o' Vigor. Start swimming and play your Aquatic Lyre, and whenever you loose stamina just twist in Jig o' Vigor fer a while, rinse and repeat. <br>    This is also useful fer finding a corpse in the water if someone were to drown (just use Lysa's Locating Lyric).<br>    Well, hope this helps out some of our rather more inexperienced swimmers out there! Now jump in the water and have some fun!!!<br><br>Dinian Arkatt<br>Lvl 21 Bard<br>Defender of the Faith<br>&nbsp;<br>Dinian Arkatt<br>Bard of the 21st Song<br>Defender of the Faith</td></tr>
